snippet.title: A Walk in the Woods
snippet.description:
Something Dark Studios is publishing a 3D spooky adventure game, where 4 players must roam a dark and dangerous forest trying to find each other while avoiding the glaze of an inhuman monster and its creatures! 

Can you find your friends before the blood moon reaches its peak and you are cursed forever? 

Want to know more? Check and like our  Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/SomethingDarkStudios/ and Instagram @SomethingDarkStudios
